[{"start": 0.0, "end": 6.88, "text": "Yes, March 17th, Tuesday, 12 or 2 am with Ito."}, {"start": 6.88, "end": 14.24, "text": "Hello, hello, we're about to make some chai because, and I'm not saying chai tea because I am cultured, unlike some people."}, {"start": 14.24, "end": 15.6, "text": "Anyway, you lost me."}, {"start": 15.6, "end": 16.8, "text": "Okay, there we go, let's resume."}, {"start": 16.8, "end": 19.84, "text": "It's so cool that it lets you edit the recording, like the name of it."}, {"start": 19.84, "end": 21.84, "text": "Why is it recording? That's really very cool."}, {"start": 22.64, "end": 25.2, "text": "Let's see what tea we've got lined up."}, {"start": 25.2, "end": 30.72, "text": "We have peppermint, jasmine green tea, the all-great tea and another peppermint."}, {"start": 30.72, "end": 31.92, "text": "Kids, what is your pick?"}, {"start": 31.92, "end": 33.2, "text": "I can make everything milky."}, {"start": 34.16, "end": 35.120000000000005, "text": "Milky's my jam."}, {"start": 35.120000000000005, "end": 37.68, "text": "Milky's good, I feel like the jasmine green tea will be good."}, {"start": 39.68, "end": 41.760000000000005, "text": "Today, you did so good today."}, {"start": 43.760000000000005, "end": 44.4, "text": "I was surprised."}, {"start": 44.4, "end": 46.72, "text": "People don't understand that I'm a great chef."}, {"start": 47.44, "end": 50.8, "text": "Like, if I took my time to cook, I was very surprised."}, {"start": 50.959999999999994, "end": 52.4, "text": "I can make food out of nothing."}, {"start": 52.4, "end": 56.16, "text": "The fact that you clocked the combination of the honey mustard and the chicken and the akibang."}, {"start": 56.16, "end": 57.599999999999994, "text": "All I had to do was see it."}, {"start": 57.599999999999994, "end": 62.239999999999995, "text": "Cool, like I was genuinely like, like Ito, like it like, it fits."}, {"start": 62.239999999999995, "end": 63.36, "text": "Of course it fits."}, {"start": 63.36, "end": 65.28, "text": "There was nothing that was more than something."}, {"start": 65.28, "end": 65.84, "text": "It was built."}, {"start": 65.84, "end": 66.8, "text": "It was perfect."}, {"start": 66.8, "end": 67.84, "text": "It was really good."}, {"start": 67.84, "end": 69.75999999999999, "text": "Yeah, I was like, it's what I enjoyed."}, {"start": 69.75999999999999, "end": 70.32, "text": "Like, yo."}, {"start": 70.32, "end": 73.67999999999999, "text": "I feel like the little things, it's like, how did you..."}, {"start": 73.67999999999999, "end": 74.72, "text": "How'd you learn this stuff?"}, {"start": 74.72, "end": 75.2, "text": "What?"}, {"start": 75.2, "end": 76.08, "text": "How'd you learn this stuff?"}, {"start": 76.32, "end": 80.88, "text": "You're not interviewing me."}, {"start": 80.88, "end": 81.52, "text": "No, no, no."}, {"start": 81.52, "end": 84.24, "text": "Yeah, I like to eat, you know, because I pick it."}, {"start": 84.24, "end": 85.67999999999999, "text": "I like to eat, so I should be able to figure it out."}, {"start": 85.67999999999999, "end": 86.96, "text": "I don't know, I just have..."}, {"start": 86.96, "end": 88.24, "text": "I always say this thing to people."}, {"start": 88.24, "end": 91.36, "text": "I actually just have a great intuition, genuinely."}, {"start": 91.92, "end": 96.48, "text": "I can guess something on the spot, not because I guessed it, but I just put..."}, {"start": 96.48, "end": 99.68, "text": "I put so many things together and it's like, in my head, I'm already calculating things."}, {"start": 99.68, "end": 101.75999999999999, "text": "And I'm like, and then you tell me, oh guess."}, {"start": 101.75999999999999, "end": 103.52, "text": "Yeah, but food is different though, man."}, {"start": 103.52, "end": 104.56, "text": "But I'm calculating."}, {"start": 104.56, "end": 105.36, "text": "I'm calculating."}, {"start": 105.36, "end": 106.88, "text": "You type with two fingers now."}, {"start": 106.88, "end": 108.72, "text": "Like, come on, it's so different."}, {"start": 108.72, "end": 110.56, "text": "You already do what you think, bro."}, {"start": 110.56, "end": 113.44, "text": "I'm calculating things, like, for guess."}, {"start": 115.03999999999999, "end": 118.64, "text": "You're the first meal I ever made was toast."}, {"start": 118.64, "end": 119.68, "text": "Who was the youngest?"}, {"start": 119.68, "end": 122.48, "text": "It was toast with strawberry jam and strawberry on top."}, {"start": 122.48, "end": 123.68, "text": "And I sent it."}, {"start": 123.68, "end": 125.52, "text": "Oh my gosh, that was good, actually."}, {"start": 125.52, "end": 126.0, "text": "I sent it."}, {"start": 126.0, "end": 130.32, "text": "If there's the right amount of strawberry jam and butter on the line, not just straight,"}, {"start": 130.32, "end": 131.2, "text": "straight up jam."}, {"start": 131.2, "end": 132.32, "text": "There was no butter though."}, {"start": 132.88, "end": 138.48, "text": "And I sent it to one of my friends and I was so proud and she said, what is that?"}, {"start": 139.6, "end": 141.12, "text": "I was so, like, shocked."}, {"start": 149.04, "end": 152.56, "text": "You know, I was scrolling, like, this morning, like half of the day."}, {"start": 154.72, "end": 156.95999999999998, "text": "Sorry, just on the topic of scrolling."}, {"start": 157.6, "end": 159.51999999999998, "text": "Do you see how I have known in social media?"}, {"start": 159.51999999999998, "end": 160.0, "text": "Yeah."}, {"start": 160.0, "end": 162.0, "text": "I don't use my phone."}, {"start": 162.08, "end": 163.2, "text": "That's so healthy."}, {"start": 163.2, "end": 165.36, "text": "I just chill out."}, {"start": 165.36, "end": 165.76, "text": "Do you?"}, {"start": 165.76, "end": 166.48, "text": "Okay, you don't."}, {"start": 166.48, "end": 168.16, "text": "We have nothing on your phone as well, huh?"}, {"start": 168.16, "end": 169.2, "text": "Just Pinterest."}, {"start": 169.2, "end": 170.8, "text": "Pinterest is just as healthy."}, {"start": 170.8, "end": 171.76, "text": "I don't even use Pinterest."}, {"start": 171.76, "end": 173.52, "text": "It just bugging me with all of those things."}, {"start": 173.52, "end": 173.92, "text": "Yeah."}, {"start": 174.56, "end": 176.08, "text": "I don't use Pinterest."}, {"start": 176.08, "end": 178.64, "text": "But it's actually so deeply overwhelming, man."}, {"start": 178.64, "end": 179.2, "text": "It is."}, {"start": 179.2, "end": 180.56, "text": "Doesn't like your brain slow down."}, {"start": 180.56, "end": 183.28, "text": "I realized my anxiety disappeared."}, {"start": 183.84, "end": 184.32, "text": "Yeah."}, {"start": 184.32, "end": 186.56, "text": "I used to have chronic anxiety."}, {"start": 186.56, "end": 187.36, "text": "Really?"}, {"start": 187.36, "end": 188.88, "text": "Yes, it's disappeared."}, {"start": 189.6, "end": 190.48, "text": "Like, all my life."}, {"start": 191.28, "end": 193.35999999999999, "text": "How were you when I first met you?"}, {"start": 193.92, "end": 194.39999999999998, "text": "How old?"}, {"start": 194.39999999999998, "end": 194.56, "text": "When?"}, {"start": 194.56, "end": 195.44, "text": "How was I?"}, {"start": 195.44, "end": 197.28, "text": "Was it present when I first met you?"}, {"start": 197.28, "end": 198.23999999999998, "text": "Of course."}, {"start": 198.23999999999998, "end": 199.35999999999999, "text": "Wow."}, {"start": 199.35999999999999, "end": 204.07999999999998, "text": "I feel like I failed to recognize it in, like, the African community."}, {"start": 204.95999999999998, "end": 210.23999999999998, "text": "Because it's portrayed so differently compared to the brown lazy community."}, {"start": 210.23999999999998, "end": 210.79999999999998, "text": "You know?"}, {"start": 210.79999999999998, "end": 212.95999999999998, "text": "Like, I'm so much better at reading it than them."}, {"start": 212.95999999999998, "end": 214.56, "text": "Well, because those are your people."}, {"start": 214.56, "end": 215.67999999999998, "text": "That's your blood, right?"}, {"start": 215.67999999999998, "end": 216.64, "text": "Yeah, I know."}, {"start": 216.64, "end": 218.0, "text": "But it's so fascinating."}, {"start": 218.0, "end": 219.83999999999997, "text": "It's the same emotion, but it's so different."}, {"start": 220.64000000000001, "end": 223.52, "text": "Like, my anxiety doesn't manifest as social anxiety."}, {"start": 223.52, "end": 224.8, "text": "Like, I'm not socially anxious."}, {"start": 224.8, "end": 226.72, "text": "That's not what I know."}, {"start": 226.72, "end": 229.6, "text": "My anxiety is brain overload."}, {"start": 230.56, "end": 233.68, "text": "I could, like, you know my anxiety to be so bad around in high school?"}, {"start": 233.68, "end": 234.8, "text": "One day, it was raining."}, {"start": 236.08, "end": 237.52, "text": "And I thought I was going to get struck by lightning."}, {"start": 238.24, "end": 238.64000000000001, "text": "Damn."}, {"start": 239.44, "end": 241.6, "text": "And I took off all my jewelry."}, {"start": 241.6, "end": 242.88, "text": "I actually look like a crazy person."}, {"start": 242.88, "end": 243.68, "text": "Like, I had a panic."}, {"start": 243.68, "end": 245.52, "text": "Like, I didn't know that was a panic attack."}, {"start": 245.52, "end": 246.08, "text": "Until I stopped."}, {"start": 246.08, "end": 246.72, "text": "So the doctor, he was like,"}, {"start": 246.72, "end": 249.44, "text": "Yeah, girl, you like literally are having like manic episodes."}, {"start": 249.44, "end": 250.32, "text": "I took off all my jewelry."}, {"start": 250.32, "end": 251.44, "text": "I took off my shoes because I was like,"}, {"start": 251.44, "end": 252.16, "text": "I have metal on it."}, {"start": 252.16, "end": 254.0, "text": "Take everything off because I'm going to get struck by lightning."}, {"start": 254.0, "end": 254.72, "text": "And I ran."}, {"start": 254.72, "end": 257.12, "text": "I bolted from the, like, hall where we had, like,"}, {"start": 257.12, "end": 259.6, "text": "our dinner from school to my, to my hostel."}, {"start": 259.6, "end": 260.08, "text": "School."}, {"start": 260.08, "end": 260.4, "text": "I was like."}, {"start": 260.4, "end": 261.2, "text": "You think you're like me?"}, {"start": 261.2, "end": 262.16, "text": "I bolted."}, {"start": 262.16, "end": 264.24, "text": "You think you're like true or good?"}, {"start": 264.24, "end": 266.4, "text": "No, I think I, I've gotten over that."}, {"start": 266.4, "end": 267.84, "text": "But yeah, I bolted."}, {"start": 267.84, "end": 270.64, "text": "I thought so many, like, manic, like, episodes where I just, like,"}, {"start": 270.64, "end": 271.44, "text": "my brain starts."}, {"start": 271.44, "end": 273.36, "text": "Like, my ex used to deal with this, like, a lot."}, {"start": 273.36, "end": 274.96, "text": "And he was, I love him."}, {"start": 275.6, "end": 277.28, "text": "So, like, he understood that."}, {"start": 277.28, "end": 278.15999999999997, "text": "He understood me."}, {"start": 278.16, "end": 280.88000000000005, "text": "And he never made me feel crazy or, like,"}, {"start": 281.68, "end": 283.44, "text": "like, what the fuck is up, like, with this crazy baby?"}, {"start": 283.44, "end": 285.28000000000003, "text": "He's just like, oh my God, like, this is happening again."}, {"start": 285.28000000000003, "end": 286.56, "text": "Like, just relax and all that."}, {"start": 287.92, "end": 289.52000000000004, "text": "But yeah, I used to have crazy, like, episodes."}, {"start": 289.52000000000004, "end": 291.20000000000005, "text": "Just like, my brain telling me all sorts of things."}, {"start": 293.68, "end": 295.20000000000005, "text": "Like, my baby can just tell me, like, right now,"}, {"start": 295.20000000000005, "end": 296.88, "text": "your mom is about to get into an accident."}, {"start": 296.88, "end": 298.48, "text": "No, she stopped kind of calling her."}, {"start": 298.96000000000004, "end": 299.44000000000005, "text": "And like, yeah."}, {"start": 300.40000000000003, "end": 302.72, "text": "But, like, ever since I stopped using my phone, I just..."}, {"start": 302.72, "end": 303.52000000000004, "text": "I know what happened."}, {"start": 303.52000000000004, "end": 305.12, "text": "How'd you, it was just the phone?"}, {"start": 305.12, "end": 305.52000000000004, "text": "It was, I..."}, {"start": 305.52000000000004, "end": 307.92, "text": "So, you've had it, like, you only stopped using your phone recently."}, {"start": 308.88000000000005, "end": 309.52000000000004, "text": "He don't get it."}, {"start": 309.52000000000004, "end": 310.40000000000003, "text": "Yep, so you knew."}, {"start": 313.44, "end": 314.32000000000005, "text": "Yeah, I knew."}, {"start": 314.32000000000005, "end": 314.96000000000004, "text": "And I changed."}, {"start": 314.96000000000004, "end": 316.16, "text": "That's crazy."}, {"start": 316.16, "end": 316.56, "text": "Wow."}, {"start": 317.44, "end": 318.64000000000004, "text": "It really is just the phone, huh?"}, {"start": 318.64000000000004, "end": 319.76000000000005, "text": "It's just the phone."}, {"start": 319.76000000000005, "end": 320.32000000000005, "text": "Really?"}, {"start": 320.32000000000005, "end": 321.92, "text": "It really is just, it's poison."}, {"start": 321.92, "end": 323.20000000000005, "text": "Yeah, no, but I think the laptop..."}, {"start": 323.20000000000005, "end": 324.24, "text": "It's chosen poison as well."}, {"start": 324.24, "end": 324.64000000000004, "text": "It's like, with you."}, {"start": 324.64000000000004, "end": 325.76000000000005, "text": "It's chosen, yeah, you could, yeah."}, {"start": 325.76000000000005, "end": 327.20000000000005, "text": "Yeah, it's like, you give someone a gun."}, {"start": 327.20000000000005, "end": 329.6, "text": "It's like, you know, how they use it."}, {"start": 330.48, "end": 330.8, "text": "Yeah."}, {"start": 331.44000000000005, "end": 332.72, "text": "I remember the first time..."}, {"start": 332.72, "end": 333.92, "text": "I said to myself, sorry, yeah."}, {"start": 335.44000000000005, "end": 336.32000000000005, "text": "How'd you come, girl?"}, {"start": 336.32000000000005, "end": 338.0, "text": "I said to myself, there's already for me to..."}, {"start": 338.08, "end": 340.56, "text": "have Instagram until I start running my TV show."}, {"start": 341.28, "end": 342.96, "text": "Then I have a reason to post."}, {"start": 342.96, "end": 345.52, "text": "And I might be going to be there, like, it's just to post."}, {"start": 345.52, "end": 346.96, "text": "Once I post, done."}, {"start": 346.96, "end": 347.68, "text": "Yeah."}, {"start": 347.68, "end": 349.28, "text": "But what am I doing on the app?"}, {"start": 349.28, "end": 349.68, "text": "Nothing."}, {"start": 350.32, "end": 351.44, "text": "I'm not promoting anything."}, {"start": 352.08, "end": 353.68, "text": "I'm not selling anything right now."}, {"start": 353.68, "end": 354.64, "text": "I'm not an influencer."}, {"start": 355.28, "end": 356.72, "text": "What am I doing on the app?"}, {"start": 356.72, "end": 357.36, "text": "Generally, no."}, {"start": 359.52, "end": 360.48, "text": "Doing your thing, man."}, {"start": 361.6, "end": 362.32, "text": "No, that makes sense."}, {"start": 362.32, "end": 363.44, "text": "I was thinking about that today as well."}, {"start": 363.44, "end": 364.32, "text": "Should I deactivate?"}, {"start": 364.96, "end": 366.0, "text": "But I didn't."}, {"start": 366.0, "end": 366.32, "text": "I don't know why."}, {"start": 366.32, "end": 368.88, "text": "If you have it used for the app, use it."}, {"start": 368.88, "end": 370.88, "text": "But then, is that all that we can use that for?"}, {"start": 370.88, "end": 372.08, "text": "For my scrolling app?"}, {"start": 372.08, "end": 373.92, "text": "You can use it on your laptop."}, {"start": 373.92, "end": 375.84, "text": "I have a version of it in my terminal."}, {"start": 375.84, "end": 376.8, "text": "Where it's just the text."}, {"start": 377.68, "end": 378.8, "text": "Yeah, you showed me that."}, {"start": 378.8, "end": 379.6, "text": "Yeah."}, {"start": 379.6, "end": 380.64, "text": "Which I haven't used in a while."}, {"start": 380.64, "end": 381.68, "text": "Why can't you just use that?"}, {"start": 381.68, "end": 382.15999999999997, "text": "I don't know."}, {"start": 382.15999999999997, "end": 382.71999999999997, "text": "I haven't been."}, {"start": 382.71999999999997, "end": 383.2, "text": "I haven't."}, {"start": 383.2, "end": 385.12, "text": "You're just scared of using your Instagram, really?"}, {"start": 385.12, "end": 385.92, "text": "Maybe."}, {"start": 385.92, "end": 386.4, "text": "Maybe."}, {"start": 386.4, "end": 386.8, "text": "You are."}, {"start": 386.8, "end": 387.76, "text": "Yeah, it's just a thing."}, {"start": 387.76, "end": 389.6, "text": "I haven't used it that much."}, {"start": 390.15999999999997, "end": 390.96, "text": "What is going on?"}, {"start": 390.96, "end": 392.08, "text": "What are those sounds?"}, {"start": 392.08, "end": 392.8, "text": "Snow clearing."}, {"start": 393.52000000000004, "end": 393.92, "text": "Okay."}, {"start": 393.92, "end": 394.48, "text": "Oh."}, {"start": 395.84000000000003, "end": 396.72, "text": "Great, a snow."}, {"start": 396.72, "end": 397.36, "text": "It's snowing."}, {"start": 399.04, "end": 399.84000000000003, "text": "What is this?"}, {"start": 399.84000000000003, "end": 400.16, "text": "Sugar."}, {"start": 401.12, "end": 402.08, "text": "I just want a new pack."}, {"start": 402.08, "end": 402.64, "text": "That's why."}, {"start": 403.2, "end": 405.04, "text": "You know, you're a very hospitable person."}, {"start": 405.04, "end": 407.04, "text": "I think it's a very beautiful treat to have."}, {"start": 407.04, "end": 408.32, "text": "Oh, thank you."}, {"start": 408.32, "end": 409.12, "text": "I got it for my mom."}, {"start": 411.44, "end": 412.72, "text": "Which I don't panic attacks, bro."}, {"start": 412.72, "end": 414.16, "text": "What was the first time I got one?"}, {"start": 414.96000000000004, "end": 415.84000000000003, "text": "Oh, I know it's..."}, {"start": 416.96000000000004, "end": 419.44, "text": "Oh, I think that the earliest one I can remember."}, {"start": 419.44, "end": 420.16, "text": "But I was like..."}, {"start": 421.12, "end": 423.04, "text": "Maybe eighth grade?"}, {"start": 423.04, "end": 424.24, "text": "Eighth grade, yeah."}, {"start": 424.24, "end": 425.12, "text": "You were just like me."}, {"start": 425.12, "end": 426.08000000000004, "text": "You said you were a kid."}, {"start": 426.08000000000004, "end": 426.56, "text": "Yeah."}, {"start": 426.56, "end": 427.68, "text": "Yeah, it's my name."}, {"start": 427.68, "end": 428.32000000000005, "text": "It was so weird."}, {"start": 428.32000000000005, "end": 429.12, "text": "I remember, I don't..."}, {"start": 429.12, "end": 430.40000000000003, "text": "Want a tiny little teacup?"}, {"start": 430.40000000000003, "end": 431.12, "text": "Yes, that's fine."}, {"start": 431.12, "end": 431.68, "text": "Let me take that."}, {"start": 431.68, "end": 432.8, "text": "Well, I'm making it the big one,"}, {"start": 432.8, "end": 434.08000000000004, "text": "but I can put it..."}, {"start": 434.08000000000004, "end": 434.72, "text": "I'll take it."}, {"start": 434.72, "end": 435.04, "text": "I'll take it."}, {"start": 435.04, "end": 435.52000000000004, "text": "Yeah, okay."}, {"start": 435.52000000000004, "end": 436.48, "text": "Yeah, okay, thank you."}, {"start": 436.48, "end": 438.08000000000004, "text": "But I remember, so I was with..."}, {"start": 440.64000000000004, "end": 441.84000000000003, "text": "My dad left for work."}, {"start": 441.84000000000003, "end": 442.40000000000003, "text": "Okay."}, {"start": 442.40000000000003, "end": 444.16, "text": "And I didn't want to go to school that day."}, {"start": 444.16, "end": 445.6, "text": "I think I was already late,"}, {"start": 445.6, "end": 447.12, "text": "like I woke up late or something."}, {"start": 447.12, "end": 448.16, "text": "And I was too nervous"}, {"start": 448.16, "end": 449.36, "text": "because I thought all the eyes"}, {"start": 449.44, "end": 450.24, "text": "were going to be on me"}, {"start": 450.24, "end": 451.68, "text": "when I went to the school."}, {"start": 452.72, "end": 456.56, "text": "And bro, I went and my mom had to like..."}, {"start": 456.56, "end": 458.96000000000004, "text": "Bro, she fought for like hours"}, {"start": 458.96000000000004, "end": 460.8, "text": "to get me to school, bro."}, {"start": 460.8, "end": 463.44, "text": "And I was crying and I was fighting."}, {"start": 463.44, "end": 465.52000000000004, "text": "It was insane, bro."}, {"start": 465.52000000000004, "end": 466.48, "text": "It was insane."}, {"start": 466.48, "end": 468.88, "text": "And I walked in and everything was fine."}, {"start": 468.88, "end": 471.12, "text": "But I think that's like my most vivid recollection"}, {"start": 471.12, "end": 472.56, "text": "of like a proper panic attack."}, {"start": 472.56, "end": 473.76, "text": "Panicking, yeah."}, {"start": 473.76, "end": 474.96000000000004, "text": "Social anxiety."}, {"start": 474.96000000000004, "end": 475.52000000000004, "text": "Yeah, man."}, {"start": 475.52000000000004, "end": 476.40000000000003, "text": "That was a big one, bro."}, {"start": 476.40000000000003, "end": 477.76, "text": "People just looking at you."}, {"start": 477.76, "end": 478.40000000000003, "text": "I'm the opposite."}, {"start": 478.4, "end": 479.44, "text": "I love you, look at me."}, {"start": 479.44, "end": 480.47999999999996, "text": "I love being late to school"}, {"start": 480.47999999999996, "end": 481.91999999999996, "text": "because I'm like, everyone gets to look at me."}, {"start": 483.12, "end": 484.56, "text": "And then I'm going to pour out the perfume."}, {"start": 484.56, "end": 487.44, "text": "You see what I mean about like the difference in anxiety?"}, {"start": 487.44, "end": 489.28, "text": "How like they come in so many different things."}, {"start": 489.28, "end": 490.15999999999997, "text": "Difference, yeah."}, {"start": 491.12, "end": 492.32, "text": "Mine is more of like,"}, {"start": 492.32, "end": 494.4, "text": "I'm the one who's scared about safety a lot."}, {"start": 496.71999999999997, "end": 497.84, "text": "Again, everything I have for my mom."}, {"start": 497.84, "end": 499.2, "text": "My mom is a very paranoid person."}, {"start": 499.91999999999996, "end": 500.96, "text": "While driving home,"}, {"start": 500.96, "end": 501.91999999999996, "text": "she's in the car behind her."}, {"start": 501.91999999999996, "end": 504.23999999999995, "text": "She's taking 10 turns before she comes to the house."}, {"start": 505.35999999999996, "end": 507.76, "text": "And I'm like, those behaviors are not normal."}, {"start": 508.64, "end": 510.32, "text": "But then he manifested it in me too."}, {"start": 510.32, "end": 511.44, "text": "I'm like, this guy is definitely phoning me"}, {"start": 511.44, "end": 512.0, "text": "and he's trying to kill me."}, {"start": 512.0, "end": 512.96, "text": "He's trying to enter my house."}, {"start": 512.96, "end": 515.6, "text": "Let's, let's keep, let's keep looking around."}, {"start": 515.6, "end": 515.92, "text": "Yup."}, {"start": 516.88, "end": 517.6, "text": "Yup, yup, yup."}, {"start": 518.88, "end": 519.2, "text": "What?"}, {"start": 520.0, "end": 521.76, "text": "Do you mind if I post this conversation on LinkedIn?"}, {"start": 522.8, "end": 523.68, "text": "Uh, what did I talk about?"}, {"start": 523.68, "end": 524.88, "text": "Panicking is actually no anchor."}, {"start": 524.88, "end": 526.88, "text": "I think that explanation is worth my mom."}, {"start": 526.88, "end": 528.96, "text": "Like as a, like you want to post a voice?"}, {"start": 528.96, "end": 531.36, "text": "It'll be like I'll post a YouTube video."}, {"start": 531.36, "end": 532.88, "text": "Well, like with the captions probably."}, {"start": 533.68, "end": 534.3199999999999, "text": "What would we talk about?"}, {"start": 534.3199999999999, "end": 535.52, "text": "Let's remember, let's remember"}, {"start": 535.52, "end": 536.4, "text": "because you know I work for the news."}, {"start": 536.4, "end": 537.12, "text": "Let's remember, let's remember."}, {"start": 538.08, "end": 538.72, "text": "What in the world?"}, {"start": 538.72, "end": 539.68, "text": "Well, how do we start?"}, {"start": 539.68, "end": 540.32, "text": "How do we start?"}, {"start": 540.32, "end": 540.48, "text": "How do we start?"}, {"start": 540.48, "end": 541.2, "text": "How do we start?"}, {"start": 541.2, "end": 544.48, "text": "How do we start?"}, {"start": 544.48, "end": 545.44, "text": "I can't believe it."}, {"start": 545.44, "end": 546.4, "text": "We'll look over it again."}, {"start": 546.4, "end": 547.68, "text": "You didn't say anything crazy."}, {"start": 547.68, "end": 549.6, "text": "Okay, I better remember how we started."}, {"start": 549.6, "end": 550.48, "text": "I just wanted to bring it up"}, {"start": 550.48, "end": 552.08, "text": "so you just have that thought going forward."}, {"start": 553.28, "end": 554.5600000000001, "text": "So we don't see anything to say."}, {"start": 555.76, "end": 556.8, "text": "But yeah, what was I going to say?"}, {"start": 558.88, "end": 559.76, "text": "Yeah, no, it was different."}, {"start": 559.76, "end": 561.92, "text": "You know, I think for me, I always like,"}, {"start": 561.92, "end": 564.24, "text": "I think I would fantasize about like the eyes."}, {"start": 564.24, "end": 565.6800000000001, "text": "Fantasize?"}, {"start": 565.6800000000001, "end": 566.72, "text": "Yeah, Mikey bro."}, {"start": 567.12, "end": 569.28, "text": "But like the eyes being kind of on me."}, {"start": 569.28, "end": 570.64, "text": "And then it's like, but when it would happen,"}, {"start": 570.64, "end": 571.36, "text": "it would be so scary."}, {"start": 571.36, "end": 572.88, "text": "So I remember with third space,"}, {"start": 572.88, "end": 574.48, "text": "the launch party that we had, bro."}, {"start": 574.48, "end": 576.08, "text": "You were so scared."}, {"start": 576.08, "end": 577.2, "text": "Bro, do you remember?"}, {"start": 577.2, "end": 578.0, "text": "I wasn't there."}, {"start": 578.0, "end": 578.8, "text": "Boo."}, {"start": 578.8, "end": 583.04, "text": "But it was like, I remember Cedric and he was like,"}, {"start": 583.04, "end": 584.72, "text": "you know, we thank you, thank you to Yishan."}, {"start": 584.72, "end": 586.0, "text": "And then I was like, oh, that's cool."}, {"start": 586.0, "end": 588.16, "text": "And then the eyes came on me and bro,"}, {"start": 588.16, "end": 591.12, "text": "I just like, it was the most nervous guy."}, {"start": 592.24, "end": 593.6800000000001, "text": "My smile and all that."}, {"start": 593.6800000000001, "end": 595.04, "text": "But I think part of that was like,"}, {"start": 595.04, "end": 596.16, "text": "I felt like I hadn't heard this"}, {"start": 596.24, "end": 598.0, "text": "at the time, my mentality was more so."}, {"start": 598.8, "end": 601.52, "text": "The quality of my work is based off the effort"}, {"start": 601.52, "end": 602.64, "text": "that I put in."}, {"start": 602.64, "end": 604.0, "text": "But which is not the case now."}, {"start": 605.4399999999999, "end": 606.7199999999999, "text": "But yeah, that was crazy."}, {"start": 608.0799999999999, "end": 609.76, "text": "The quality of my work is based off the results"}, {"start": 609.76, "end": 610.8, "text": "that I gave to you."}, {"start": 610.8, "end": 612.3199999999999, "text": "Exactly, it's all results man."}, {"start": 612.3199999999999, "end": 615.12, "text": "Like effort is not, it doesn't really mean anything."}, {"start": 615.68, "end": 617.6, "text": "You put in all the effort into the wrong thing"}, {"start": 617.6, "end": 618.64, "text": "and then just get nothing."}, {"start": 627.12, "end": 630.16, "text": "In Pakistan, we have this thing called Kashmiri."}, {"start": 630.9599999999999, "end": 631.92, "text": "Kashmiri?"}, {"start": 631.92, "end": 632.64, "text": "Kashmiri."}, {"start": 633.28, "end": 634.0, "text": "From Kashmir."}, {"start": 635.8399999999999, "end": 638.0, "text": "And it is a pink tea with pistachios."}, {"start": 638.0, "end": 640.0799999999999, "text": "And it is absolutely delicious."}, {"start": 641.36, "end": 643.36, "text": "Maybe I should have something in my room, you know."}, {"start": 644.3199999999999, "end": 645.68, "text": "You do not have to eat a room."}, {"start": 645.68, "end": 647.04, "text": "I have nothing in my room, bro."}, {"start": 647.04, "end": 649.04, "text": "I have like, I don't really."}, {"start": 649.04, "end": 649.52, "text": "You do."}, {"start": 649.52, "end": 650.0799999999999, "text": "Piss off."}, {"start": 650.0799999999999, "end": 651.68, "text": "Right, I brought some cold."}, {"start": 651.68, "end": 652.88, "text": "Yeah, you're right, you know."}, {"start": 652.88, "end": 653.8399999999999, "text": "I jam sometimes."}, {"start": 654.88, "end": 655.68, "text": "I play football."}, {"start": 657.12, "end": 659.52, "text": "Yeah, maybe I should, I should get into that more, you know."}, {"start": 661.76, "end": 664.3199999999999, "text": "Don't like overcommit to eat your life though."}, {"start": 664.3199999999999, "end": 665.6, "text": "Yeah, yeah, no, it's simple."}, {"start": 665.6, "end": 666.0799999999999, "text": "Very simple."}, {"start": 666.0799999999999, "end": 667.28, "text": "But tea is good to have though."}, {"start": 667.28, "end": 669.68, "text": "Something to be able to host people, you know."}, {"start": 670.88, "end": 671.68, "text": "Thank you so much."}, {"start": 671.68, "end": 672.3199999999999, "text": "Should tell you."}, {"start": 672.3199999999999,