rt": 723.92, "end": 724.96, "text": "Wait, the Sachi is really good."}, {"start": 725.84, "end": 727.12, "text": "I didn't try it, I just tried it."}, {"start": 729.52, "end": 730.4, "text": "But um."}, {"start": 730.4, "end": 732.0, "text": "We know if you want any more."}, {"start": 732.0, "end": 732.64, "text": "I will, yeah."}, {"start": 733.36, "end": 737.68, "text": "But it's called ras, which is like biscuits, like thick biscuits."}, {"start": 737.68, "end": 739.4399999999999, "text": "And you dip those in tea specifically."}, {"start": 739.4399999999999, "end": 740.3199999999999, "text": "Like they're meant to be dipped."}, {"start": 740.3199999999999, "end": 741.4399999999999, "text": "Yeah, thick, okay."}, {"start": 741.4399999999999, "end": 742.88, "text": "Like bigger, those are nice."}, {"start": 742.88, "end": 743.28, "text": "Yeah."}, {"start": 743.28, "end": 745.4399999999999, "text": "But like people dip like rice crime."}, {"start": 745.4399999999999, "end": 748.0, "text": "Like bro, this thing is just melting into the tea at this point."}, {"start": 748.0, "end": 749.12, "text": "Like come and be serious."}, {"start": 754.16, "end": 755.52, "text": "This milk is a game changer."}, {"start": 756.48, "end": 757.76, "text": "You guys have it in Rwanda, right?"}, {"start": 757.76, "end": 758.56, "text": "Like clouded milk."}, {"start": 759.52, "end": 760.96, "text": "I don't know, I haven't tried clouded milk."}, {"start": 760.96, "end": 762.0, "text": "Rwanda's big on tea though."}, {"start": 762.0, "end": 764.08, "text": "I think one of their main exports is tea."}, {"start": 764.08, "end": 764.56, "text": "Tea, yeah, yeah."}, {"start": 768.16, "end": 769.76, "text": "Do you know what the cracker is?"}, {"start": 769.76, "end": 771.76, "text": "The, ah, it's tea's good old."}, {"start": 771.76, "end": 772.4, "text": "It's so good."}, {"start": 772.88, "end": 773.28, "text": "Hot leg?"}, {"start": 775.4399999999999, "end": 776.16, "text": "What's that?"}, {"start": 776.16, "end": 777.52, "text": "It's like a little cake thing."}, {"start": 777.52, "end": 777.84, "text": "Yeah."}, {"start": 777.84, "end": 779.2, "text": "Oh, you're stacked, huh?"}, {"start": 780.48, "end": 782.4, "text": "I have like good snacks."}, {"start": 782.4, "end": 783.4399999999999, "text": "You need perfect snacks."}, {"start": 783.4399999999999, "end": 784.48, "text": "Wonderful snacks."}, {"start": 784.48, "end": 784.96, "text": "Yeah."}, {"start": 784.96, "end": 804.64, "text": "I actually need a rich husband."}, {"start": 804.64, "end": 805.76, "text": "To buy his snacks?"}, {"start": 805.76, "end": 806.08, "text": "No."}, {"start": 808.24, "end": 812.96, "text": "Because ain't no way I'm doing this for somebody who is not like."}, {"start": 815.2800000000001, "end": 817.52, "text": "In a way, I'm like pampering your life."}, {"start": 817.52, "end": 819.36, "text": "I feel like you do hampering you."}, {"start": 819.36, "end": 819.9200000000001, "text": "God, that's not."}, {"start": 819.9200000000001, "end": 820.64, "text": "I do it for my friends."}, {"start": 820.64, "end": 822.32, "text": "Yeah, because I don't expect anything from my friends."}, {"start": 822.32, "end": 823.44, "text": "Like my friends are my friends."}, {"start": 824.24, "end": 828.64, "text": "They are going to take time, take times with me."}, {"start": 828.64, "end": 830.96, "text": "But my partner, like why don't I just come as a guy"}, {"start": 830.96, "end": 833.2800000000001, "text": "and just balance and you just be like, oh, there."}, {"start": 833.2800000000001, "end": 834.08, "text": "What are you doing?"}, {"start": 836.08, "end": 840.5600000000001, "text": "And you want to be, to be your wife and be locked up in your house"}, {"start": 840.5600000000001, "end": 842.72, "text": "and nothing to show for it."}, {"start": 842.88, "end": 845.6, "text": "Sometimes I stress about like, maybe I'm not in the right"}, {"start": 845.6, "end": 847.2, "text